{"tid":1323754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾庭耀民調 以評分計鄺俊宇最高　李慧琼、葉劉、梁美芬急跌","createTime":"2019-07-16T10:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T11:22:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2b781eedef76bb016a40b00feccbe69c8bb72c8d","tid":1323754,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGQ5sdW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGQ5sdW.png&h=42018de3&s={SIZE}\" />鍾庭耀領導的香港民意研究所脫離港大獨立運作後，公布首份民意研究結果，<strong><ins>認知度最高</ins></strong>的 6 名議員，分別是楊岳橋、毛孟靜、李慧琼、葉劉淑儀、梁美芬和鄺俊宇。<ins><strong>若以評分排行</strong></ins>，最高分是鄺俊宇 61.6 分，楊岳橋以 57.4 分排第二，毛孟靜 47.4 分第三。<br />\n<br />\n建制派方面，三名上榜議員認知度都超過 90％，其中葉劉淑儀的認知度更高達 97.1％，但三人都較今年 3 月調查評分急跌，李慧琼評分 33.5 分，跌了 9.9 分；葉劉淑儀 33.5 分，跌了 15.2 分；梁美芬是 6 名認知度最高的議員中評分最低，只有 27.1 分，比上次調查跌了 11.8 分。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所表示，在本月 5 日至 8 日，訪問了 500 多名市民，被訪者可在無提示下，講出最多 10 名最熟悉的議員，得出認知度最高的 6 位，然後再為作評分調查，由於最終認知度最低的議員會再剔除，再得出五大議員，所以在評分中最高的鄺俊宇，因認知度最低，無到入五大議員中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%8D%E7%9F%A5%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98-6-%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98-%E6%9D%8E%E6%85%A7%E7%90%BC-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC%E6%80%A5%E8%B7%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598-6-%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25AE%2587%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2590%25BC-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258A%25AC%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25B7%258C%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=336c9b90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598-6-%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25AE%2587%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2590%25BC-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258A%25AC%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25B7%258C%2F&h=041b9aec\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%8D%E7%9F%A5%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98-6-%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98-%E6%9D%8E%E6%85%A7%E7%90%BC-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC%E6%80%A5%E8%B7%8C/</a>"},{"pid":"377f6dd0b5cb482728806ec39093533fc4088a7d","tid":1323754,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"竟然冇譚文豪"}]}